<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>8 SPEED, 9 SPEED, AND 13 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON SERIES - INSTALL - SHIFTER HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>SHIFTER HOUSING</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place all three mainshaft sliding clutches in the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cm">Figure 424</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cm" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cm" filename="../figg13/g13018cm.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 423. Place Mainshaft Sliding Clutches in Neutral Position</caption>
            </figure>
            <para>Install shifter housing gasket in position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018cn">Figure 425</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018cn" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018cn" filename="../figg13/g13018cn.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 424. Install Shifter Housing Gasket in Position</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">With all three shift yokes in the neutral position, install the shifter housing assembly on
                the case, fitting the shift yokes into the slots of the corresponding sliding clutches.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Avoid tilting assembly during installation as the three sets of tension springs and balls are
                        free to be released from the bores in the top of the housing.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Loctite 242 to the bolt threads. Install the bolts in the housing and tighten to 35 to
                45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 Nm) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018co">Figure 426</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018co" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018co" filename="../figg13/g13018co.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 425. Install Bolts in Housing and ></caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
